Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, bagaimana kalau saat liburan\Nkita semua ke pantai?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku juga berniat untuk pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.\NAharen juga ingin pergi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita barbeku juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi barbeku di pantai\Nbersama teman, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang yang berbahagia\Ndi dunia nyata ini sangat sibuk, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.79,0:00:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tamanaha, kau mau ikut juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, betul.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku juga boleh ikut ke pantai?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh ikut memanggang daging juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah memutuskan mau ke pantai mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.77,0:01:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pulau terpencil...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.53,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, coba jelaskan lebih detail\Ntentang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.24,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pulau yang bisa didatangi\Npulang-pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.72,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Nanti kita berangkat dengan perahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kita pulang,\Nmenggunakan perahu terakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa main lumayan lama, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan cuman itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana juga adalah power spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya, pasangan yang melihat\Nmatahari terbenam
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,di cakrawala dari pulau ini bersama,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.83,0:02:58.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan terus bersama untuk waktu yang lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.57,0:03:02.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah matahari terbenam pun sepertinya\Nakan sempat untuk naik perahu terakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersama untuk waktu lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh! Aharen sepertinya tertarik!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aharen sepertinya sangat menantikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu pasti karena hal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aharen sebenarnya adalah
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,reinkarnasi dari Robinson Crusoe!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti mahir dalam hal\Nyang berhubungan dengan bertahan hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.53,0:03:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu di pulau kecil yang terbatas makanannya\Ntentu saja laut menjadi sumber makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,membeli pakaian renang yang bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakaian renang?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak kusangka semuanya\Ntak punya pakaian renang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanya punya pakaian renang sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.83,0:04:05.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau yang seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakaian renang yang kelihatan pusar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum pernah pakai yang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah tidak akan aneh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa! Tenang saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya untuk pergi ke pantai juga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kita coba yang berbeda dari biasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tamanaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.38,0:04:35.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kupikir yang seperti ini\Nakan cocok dengan Tamanaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga! Imut, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biar kucoba.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya mempunyai pakaian renang\Nuntuk lomba saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah bisa belanja dengan yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga, sekolah lamaku\Ntak ada kolam renangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku bahkan tidak punya\Npakaian renang sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.83,0:04:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, yang ini juga imut!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya menyenangkan bisa dekat dengan\Nsemuanya sambil berbelanja pakaian renang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menginginkan hal seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kalian bisa dekat denganku\Nyang murid pindahan ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku sangat berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.23,0:05:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke depannya pun mari kita lakukan\Nberbagai hal bersama, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.37,0:05:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk Ooshiro, bagaimana kalau\Npakaian renang yang begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gayanya bagus, jadi mungkin akan cocok.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.03,0:05:27.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, eh... bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.18,0:05:40.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua pakaiannya cocok!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah! Imutnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat cocok!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.63,0:05:55.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh iya. Karena sudah dipakai,\Nmari kita foto pakaian renangnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang seperti ini juga cocok, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ahachan seperti idola!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah berpose!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah difoto aku kirim ke Raidou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang bagus?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pakaian renang pria itu jenisnya\Nsedikit dan terlalu mahal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang seperti ini bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ambil dulu makannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaraknya terlalu dekat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.16,0:06:43.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei Aharen, mundur, mundur.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.40,0:06:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang ini aku tak tahu\Ndia ada di mananya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, sekarang kau terlalu jauh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.40,0:06:58.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau menjauh sampai mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanti saja aku simpan ini\Nsetelah sampai di pantai.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya, Satou.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah menemaniku memilih bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.52,0:07:14.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.00,0:07:18.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunjukkan perubahan dirimu\Ndi musim panas ini pada Raidou!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu, Satou...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku takut akan perubahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:34.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau suatu saat hubunganku\Ndengan Raidou pun ikut berubah?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.23,0:07:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama kalian berjumpa, Aharen dan Raidou\Njuga sudah sama-sama banyak berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru karena berubah\Nmaka ada sekarang ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau bilang begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.97,0:07:57.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dirimu sendiri juga harus berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak usah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.37,0:08:09.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pulaunya sudah dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cukup besar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baru pertama pergi ke pulau.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di dekat tempat kita berlabuh ada pantai.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak sabar, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.87,0:08:26.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini Kak Reina tidak ada?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.93,0:08:33.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia pergi jalan-jalan dengan Raidou.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Padahal Ren juga mau ikut.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bicara begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.17,0:08:43.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya dia pergi dengan teman sekolahnya\Nyang lain juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah, hari ini main dengan Eru, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.43,0:08:53.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Dia pergi bermain\Ndengan temannya tanpa alasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat tidak elegan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.77,0:09:00.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi agar aku bisa segera menyusul\Nke pulau itu jika terjadi sesuatu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus mempersiapkan segalanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku mengejarnya dengan helikopter,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,apakah di pulau itu ada landasan helikopter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus memastikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.40,0:09:12.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak,\Nmungkin aku harus menyewa perahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk detailnya aku harus tanya\Npada pekerja di pulau itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.82,0:09:20.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Eru, ayo kita menonton film.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini seram sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Reina di pulau itu seperti itu juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Festival aneh di desa pedalaman
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.83,0:10:01.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang bisa saja ada di pulau kecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Festival aneh dan berbahaya\Nyang sudah turun-temurun.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia diculik untuk hal tersebut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Laut!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh! Raidou!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Stelan renangmu bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf menunggu lama!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aneh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat imut sampai aku kehilangan kata-kata.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau beli yang baru, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah berapa tahun yang lalu\Nkau lihat yang sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat imut.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kita pulang-pergi,\Njadi, waktunya pendek.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, cepat kita bermain!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putar-putar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putar-putar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.67,0:11:58.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kiri.\N- Kanan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang mana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dagingnya alot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya mau bagaimana lagi, daging murah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musim panas, laut.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Laki-laki dan perempuan, serta barbeku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sekarang bagian dari orang\Nyang berbahagia di dunia nyata!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daging orang yang berbahagia\Ndi dunia nyata terlalu enak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.24,0:12:51.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, sudah mendung.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kita tak bisa melihat\Nmatahari terbenam, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Banyak hal menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bersyukur bisa datang bersama kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah saatnya perahu berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.82,0:13:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu, perahu yang akan kita tumpangi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.53,0:13:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku salah melihat jam perahunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terakhir
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,baru saja berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serius.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan dimarahi ibuku!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kami ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,John Manjirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manjirou dan lainnya yang terdampar
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,sampai penyelamat datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu Manjirou diselamatkan\Noleh perahu Amerika.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.83,0:14:20.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menghasilkan banyak uang di Amerika\Ndan kembali pulang ke Jepang,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi apakah mungkin aku bisa seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,(Jangan sentuh umbi yang kau galih)\NHot taimo iji runa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mahir bahasa Inggris!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.57,0:14:33.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, harus belajar\Nbahasa Inggris dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.14,0:14:35.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ingin melakukan ini asalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.03,0:14:40.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang kau ada pilihan lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita menginap di penginapan pulau ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Menginap?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ternyata ada orang yang tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita beli keperluan dulu\Ndi minimarket.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata cukup berkembang juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf menunggu lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami ketinggalan perahu pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini, kami akan\Nmenginap semalam di pulau.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Reina akan menginap di pulau,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.63,0:15:19.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia tidak akan pulang hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena pulau ini cukup berkembang,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, sepertinya akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, ada Kak Raidou juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.73,0:15:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya, jadi tidak bisa pulang\Nkarena salahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, kita menemukan penginapan\Nyang murah juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, di sini adalah kamar laki-laki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pasti pulang besok!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena temanku sudah datang,\Njadi, aku matikan dulu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.43,0:16:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bilang teman begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.20,0:16:07.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah aku terlalu besar kepala?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang tuamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dimarahi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.33,0:16:15.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku juga tiba-tiba menginap\Nseperti ini bersama kami malam ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau tidak keberatan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.63,0:16:18.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru rasanya bagai mimpi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Barusan kau memanggilku Riku?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal sebelumnya masih Tamanaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya kalau begitu lebih cocok saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,sangat bahagia!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini berlebihan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita mandi bersama yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku ikut merencanakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.40,0:16:57.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, meskipun Riku lumayan kena marah tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.23,0:17:00.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi rasanya menyenangkan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.23,0:17:01.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kalau kalian senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana hari ini menurutmu, Aharen?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat imut sampai aku kehilangan kata-kata.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini juga berkat Satou.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah,\Naku hanya mendorongmu maju saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu semua berkat Aharen memberanikan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enak, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aharen bisa berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imut.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imut, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat imut.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak dulu, aku
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Eru, kalau dulu\Nmungkin sudah pergi ke pulau itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tidak apa-apa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.14,0:18:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku tidak bisa\Nselalu ada bersama Reina.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.03,0:18:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga harus mendewasakan diri\Ndengan menjauh dari Reina.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Eru, kau berubah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ren juga harus sedikit berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah bisa mandi sendirian, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.60,0:18:32.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habisnya, kalau tidak ada Kak Reina,\Nrumah rasanya kosong dan sepi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, ya, Kak Eru.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sayang Kakak!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga sama, Ren.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini temani aku tidur bersama, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.40,0:18:47.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya, jadi seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat kita berkemah dulu,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita juga tidur bersebelahan\Nseperti ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.80,0:19:09.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat suka sisimu yang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu berterima kasih padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raidou.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus menjadi bahagia\Nbersama Aharen, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.83,0:19:24.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih gelap.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terbangun di jam yang tak biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raidou.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aharen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.\NAku membangunkanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah bangun, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matahari, cakrawala...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,berdekatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun kita tidak melihat\Nmatahari terbenam,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak masalah diganti matahari pagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bersyukur bisa melihatnya berdua.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.47,0:20:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita berdua, apakah akan selalu bisa\Nterus bersama tanpa berubah?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.17,0:20:58.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa manusia itu adalah\Nhal yang pasti berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.93,0:21:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maka dari itu, perubahan ke arah baik\Nmaupun arah buruk,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagaimanapun itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku ingin kita bisa terus bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takut pulang ke rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.57,0:21:31.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti ibu akan sangat marah padaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.83,0:21:33.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, sudah mau pulang, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun terjadi berbagai hal,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.53,0:21:39.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyenangkan, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.83,0:21:40.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.37,0:21:44.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, masih belum berakhir!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, kita bermain di pantai sekali lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu? Kau ini, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kita terlambat lebih dari ini,\Naku tak tahu akan bagaimana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kan kita bisa pulang pakai perahu yang sore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.63,0:21:58.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, ayo kita bermain lebih banyak!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betul juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang hebat, Raidou!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Langsung mengerti maksudku!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.99,0:22:05.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.03,0:22:07.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.18,0:22:11.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi jam perahunya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak. Kalau akan dimarahi\Nbagaimanapun juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.43,0:22:21.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Riku juga ikut!
